# Neovim Undo Directory

This directory is automatically created by Neovim configuration to store persistent undo files.

## Purpose
- **Persistent Undo**: Maintains undo history between editing sessions
- **Data Recovery**: Allows undoing changes even after reopening files
- **Enhanced Workflow**: Provides advanced undo capabilities across sessions

## Management
- Automatically managed by Neovim
- Undo files persist until manually deleted or configuration changes
- Provides powerful undo/redo capabilities across file close/reopen cycles

This directory exists to ensure the undo directory structure is maintained in the repository.
